59,How do you stay patient when someone is struggling to express themselves?,ai,"- Listen actively, empathetically and without judgment. Sometimes people struggle to express themselves due to a lack of confidence, fear of being wrong, or a feeling of being overwhelmed. By actively listening and showing empathy, I can help the person feel more comfortable and confident in their ability to communicate their thoughts and feelings.

